Mean Creek;;82;;89;;R;;Quiet adolescent Sam (Rory Culkin) has been bullied by George (Josh Peck), a fellow student who has trouble fitting in with other teens. When Rocky (Trevor Morgan), Sam's elder brother, finds out Sam is being picked on, he enlists his buddies to help get back at George. They ask George to accompany them on a boating expedition deep in the woods, but when their plan to humiliate George horrifically backfires, the friends make a series of poor decisions that will change their lives.;;Drama;;Jacob Aaron Estes;;2004;;Rory Culkin,Ryan Kelley,Scott Mechlowicz,Trevor Morgan,Josh Peck,Carly Schroeder,Branden Williams,Raissa Fleming;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mean_creek